    "name": "Metformin vs Watchful Waiting: T2DM Progression Risk (CohortMethod)",
    "description": "Propensity-score matched cohort study estimating the hazard ratio for Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus progression in prediabetic patients initiating metformin versus those managed with watchful waiting. Uses 1:1 nearest-neighbour matching on logit PS with 0.2 SD caliper. Covariates: demographics, conditions, drug exposures, measurements, procedures — all in 365-day baseline window. Negative control outcomes recommended for empirical calibration.",
